    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/545000094/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """The subject '' History of Urban Law and the planning of Madrid '' is an optional subject offered to undergraduate students in Building.
In this subject we analyze the development and evolution of the city of Madrid. Beeing a subject taught online, does not require the physical presence of students in class. However, it is offered the possibility of going to seminars, conferences and guided tours in Madrid .
Likewise, being a subject taught in the English language is sought through it, implement the knowledge of the English language."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/pilarcristina.izquierdo%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés/Castellano"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/ma.florez%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/pilarcristina.izquierdo%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "History Of Urban Law And Planning Of Madrid"@es .

